definition: to forward goods/to ship/to distribute/transshipment/a lucky break/change of fortune (for the better)
to revolve/to turn/to circle about/to walk about/classifier for revolutions (per minute etc): revs, rpm/classifier for repeated actions
to turn/to change direction/to transfer/to forward (mail)
storage depot on a transportation route

sentences.english: Consider the recent opening of the new, expanded Fairview Container Terminal at the Port of Prince Rupert.
sentences.chinese: 最近在鲁伯特王子岛港新开通了怡景集装箱转运站。

sentences.english: Two of the seriously injured were transferred to a better hospital for treatment of medical conditions.
sentences.chinese: 其中两名重伤员被转运到医疗条件更好的医院治疗。

sentences.english: Freight prepaid to Buenos aires in transit to Asuncion Paraguay.
sentences.chinese: 运费付至布宜诺斯艾利斯，再转运到巴拉圭的亚松森。

sentences.english: And we also have the possibility of offering the services of a supply vessel.
sentences.chinese: 拼箱货船货转运以及供应船的服务。

sentences.english: Please amend your L/C to allow partial shipment and transhipment.
sentences.chinese: 请修改你方信用证允许分批装运与转运。

sentences.english: Some of the first batch of imperial treasures being transfered, 1937.
sentences.chinese: 1937年，首批帝王宝藏中的一些被转运。

sentences.english: Objective TO investigate the alteration of ion transport across the colonic epithelium in the rat descending colon applying by benzalkonium chloride (BAC).
sentences.chinese: 目的探讨苯扎氯铵对大鼠降结肠上皮离子转运的影响。

sentences.english: ii. A bill of lading indicating that transhipment will or may take place is acceptable, even if the credit prohibits transhipment
sentences.chinese: 银行可以接受注明将要发生或可能发生转运的提单。

sentences.english: We have been able to transship cargoes at Hong Kong.
sentences.chinese: 货物如果转运，我们得多付运费。

sentences.english: The renal proximal tubule is the primary site of carrier-mediated transport from blood to urine.
sentences.chinese: 近端肾小管是由血到尿媒介转运的一个特定部位。

sentences.english: Inhibited transport and sequestration to the vacuoles were reasonable.
sentences.chinese: 其中，抑制转运和隔离到液胞较为合理。

sentences.english: There is an elevator connecting it's transit zone with technical and packaging areas in the basement.
sentences.chinese: 电梯连接转运区和地下室的技术及包装区。

sentences.english: We hope you can make a direct shipment as any transshipment will delay the arrival of goods .
sentences.chinese: 希望贵方能采用直运方式，因为转运会耽误货期。

sentences.english: This paper reviews possible role of transporters in paraquat resistance.
sentences.chinese: 本文主要综述了转运体在百草枯抗性中的可能作用。

sentences.english: Arrange for transshipment en route if necessary.
sentences.chinese: 如果有必要的话，安排货物在途中的转运。
